{
  "abstract": "Land and water are the key elements of the\r\nresource-base of rainfed farming systems and strategies\r\nfor effective management of these resources are\r\nintimately linked. This paper reviews ICRISAT's\r\nresearch approach for developing improved land and\r\nwater management practices and their integration with\r\nother aspects of farming systems. The small\r\nwatershed-based farming systems approach which holds s\r\ngood promise for management of Vertisols is discussed.\r\nThe present status of research on.Alfisol management,\r\ntank irrigation and runoff modeling,at.ICRISAT has been\r\nreviewed\r\n",
